    <item>
      <title>Mantrapushpam - मन्त्रपुष्पं</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/mantra-pushpam/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/mantra-pushpam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/Vishnu.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;मन्त्रपुष्पं 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AA&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AA&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Mantra Pushpam 
    &lt;div id=&#34;mantra-pushpam&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#mantra-pushpam&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ॐ यो॑ऽपां पुष्पं॒ वेद॑।  पुष्प॑वान् प्र॒जावा᳚न् पशु॒मान् भ॑वति ।&lt;br&gt;
च॒न्द्रमा॒ वा अ॒पां पुष्पम्᳚।  पुष्प॑वान् प्र॒जावा᳚न् पशु॒मान् भ॑वति ।&lt;br&gt;
य ए॒वं वेद॑ । यो॑ऽपामा॒यत॑नं॒ वेद॑ । आ॒यत॑नवान् भवति ॥ १॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;अ॒ग्निर्वा अ॒पामा॒यत॑नम्।  आ॒यत॑नवान् भवति ।&lt;br&gt;
यो᳚ऽग्नेरा॒यतनं॒ वेद॑ । आ॒यत॑नवान् भवति ।&lt;br&gt;
आपो॒ वा अ॒ग्नेरा॒यत॑नम् ।  आ॒यत॑नवान् भवति ।&lt;br&gt;
य ए॒वं वेद॑ । यो॑ऽपामा॒यत॑नं॒ वेद॑ । आ॒यत॑नवान् भवति ॥ २॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Rigvedoktam Devisuktam - ऋग्वेदोक्तं देवीसूक्तम्</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/rigvedoktam-devisuktam/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/rigvedoktam-devisuktam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/Durga.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;ऋग्वेदोक्तं देवीसूक्तम् 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%8B%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%8B%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Rigvedoktam Devisuktam 
    &lt;div id=&#34;rigvedoktam-devisuktam&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#rigvedoktam-devisuktam&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;॥विनियोगः॥&lt;br&gt;
ॐ अहमित्यष्टर्चस्य सूक्तस्य वागाम्भृणी ऋषिः,&lt;br&gt;
सच्चित्सुखात्मकः सर्वगतः परमात्मा देवता, द्वितीयाया ॠचो&lt;br&gt;
जगती, शिष्टानां त्रिष्टुप् छन्दः, देवीमाहात्म्यपाठे विनियोगः।*&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;॥ध्यानम्॥&lt;br&gt;
ॐ सिंहस्था शशिशेखरा मरकतप्रख्यैश्‍चतुर्भिर्भुजैः&lt;br&gt;
शङ्खं चक्रधनुःशरांश्‍च दधती नेत्रैस्त्रिभिः शोभिता।&lt;br&gt;
आमुक्ताङ्गदहारकङ्कणरणत्काञ्चीरणन्नूपुरा&lt;br&gt;
दुर्गा दुर्गतिहारिणी भवतु नो रत्‍‌नोल्लसत्कुण्डला॥*&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;॥देवीसूक्तम्*॥&lt;br&gt;
ॐ अ॒हं रु॒द्रेभि॒र्वसु॑भिश्चराम्य॒हमा᳚दि॒त्यैरु॒त वि॒श्वदे᳚वैः ।&lt;br&gt;
अ॒हं मि॒त्रावरु॑णो॒भा बि॑भर्म्य॒हमि᳚न्द्रा॒ग्नी अ॒हम॒श्विनो॒भा ॥ १ ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Yaksha Prashna - यक्षप्रश्ना:</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/yaksha-prashna/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/yaksha-prashna/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/SanskritYatra-Subhashitam.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;यक्षप्रश्ना: 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%A8&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%A8&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Yaksha Prashna 
    &lt;div id=&#34;yaksha-prashna&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#yaksha-prashna&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;यक्षप्रश्ना:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;पाण्डवानां वनवाससमय:| एकदा एक: ब्राह्मण: तेषां समीपम् आगत्य एकं हरिणं ग्रहीतुं साह्हायं याचयति। तस्य हवनीयसामग्री: हरिणेन चोरिता:| सर्वे भ्रातर: प्रयत्नं कुर्वन्ति, किन्तु मृगं न पश्यन्ति| पिपासिता: सर्वे वृक्षस्य अध: विश्रमन्ति।&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;तस्मिन् समये कनिष्ठ: नकुल: वृक्षं आरूढ्य पश्यति। एकं जलाशयं(पुष्करं) पश्यति। जलम् आनेतुं गच्छति। किञ्चित् समयानन्तरम् अपि न प्रत्यागच्छति। अनन्तरं सहदेव: गच्छति, स: अपि न प्रत्यागच्छति। तदनन्तरं भीम: अर्जुन: च गच्छत:। अन्ते युधिष्ठिर: गच्छति। सर्वे भ्रातर: पुष्करस्य समीपे भूमौ पतिता:।&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Gitanjali - गीतांजली</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/geetanjali/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/geetanjali/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/MySamskrutYatra-min.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;गीतांजली 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B2&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B2&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Geetanjali 
    &lt;div id=&#34;geetanjali&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#geetanjali&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;यत्र मनः भयरहितमस्ति शिरः च उन्नतमस्ति&lt;br&gt;
यत्र ज्ञानम् मुक्तम् प्रवहति&lt;br&gt;
यत्र सङ्कीर्ण-प्राकारैह् सम्सारः भग्नः न अभवत्&lt;br&gt;
यत्र पदानि ह्इदयगाम्भिर्यतः आगच्छति&lt;br&gt;
यत्र श्रान्तरहितॊद्यमम् पूर्णतॊन्मुखमस्ति&lt;br&gt;
यत्र बुधिधारायाः मार्गभ्रम्शम् निर्जन-मरुभुम्याम् न अभवत्&lt;br&gt;
यत्र मनः भवता प्रकर्ष्यते विशालचिन्तनाय कर्माय च&lt;br&gt;
मुक्तेह् तत्-स्वर्गार्थम् मम राष्ट्रमुधरॆत्&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Vairagya Shatakam - वैराग्यशतकम्</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/vairagyashatakam/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/vairagyashatakam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/Upanishad.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;वैराग्यशतकम् 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%AE&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
