    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;उद्यमेनैव सिध्यन्ति कार्याणि न मनोरथैः ।&lt;br&gt;
न हि सुप्तस्य सिंहस्य प्रविशन्ति मुखे मृगाः ।।&lt;br&gt;
Meaning: Success in life can be achieved only by hard work and not by merely wishing for it. No animal will enter into the mouth of a lion that is sleeping.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
