    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In English we can call it Hymn of Creation. This is part of 10th mandala of the Rigveda (10:129). It is contemplating on the cosmology and the origin of the universe. This is one of the oldest text from Bhartiya Rishis. It has only 7 slokas and it goes like following.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
